# Code ownership by architectural layer (ADR-0013).
#
# Routes review by layer/domain: platform -> leads, each domain -> its owner,
# shells -> leads. Last matching pattern wins, so the order is general -> specific.
#
# Paths use the CURRENT (flat) crate layout. When crates are relocated into
# crates/{platform,domains,shells}/ (migration phase 5) replace these with the
# folder globs noted at the bottom.

# Default: leads own everything not otherwise claimed.
*                                   @schiste

# --- Platform (leads) -------------------------------------------------------
/crates/sp42-types/                 @schiste
/crates/sp42-core/                  @schiste
/crates/sp42-coordination/          @schiste
/crates/sp42-wiki/                  @schiste
/crates/sp42-live/                  @schiste
/crates/sp42-reporting/             @schiste
/crates/sp42-inference/             @schiste

# --- Domains (domain owners) ------------------------------------------------
# Each domain folder is owned by that domain's maintainer. Until sp42-patrol /
# sp42-citation are extracted (migration phases 3-4) the patrol and citation code
# lives in sp42-core above. Add the owner here when the domain crate lands:
# /crates/domains/patrolling/        @patrol-owner
# /crates/domains/references/        @citation-owner

# --- Shells (leads) ---------------------------------------------------------
/crates/sp42-cli/                   @schiste
/crates/sp42-app/                   @schiste
/crates/sp42-desktop/               @schiste
/crates/sp42-server/                @schiste
/crates/sp42-devtools/              @schiste

# --- Governance / enforcement (leads) ---------------------------------------
/CONSTITUTION.md                    @schiste
/GOVERNANCE.md                      @schiste
/docs/platform/adr/                 @schiste
/.github/                           @schiste
/scripts/check-layering.sh          @schiste

# --- Post-relocation layout (migration phase 5) -----------------------------
# /crates/platform/**                @schiste
# /crates/domains/patrolling/**      @patrol-owner
# /crates/domains/references/**      @citation-owner
# /crates/shells/**                  @schiste
